      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is suitable for someone looking for a functional car at a more affordable price point. While it runs and drives, there are visible signs of wear on both the interior and exterior, and it may require some minor mechanical attention or cosmetic touch-ups in the near future. It has been a dependable driver, but it is no longer in its prime. Expect a vehicle that is reliable for basic transportation but shows its age.",
