      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, maintained to an uncompromising showroom standard. This vehicle features a flawless exterior finish and a pristine, meticulously preserved interior. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands absolute perfection, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 46500.0,
