    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. I\u2019ve babied this car since the day I got it, and it is in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014it still has that 'new car' feel! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and runs like an absolute dream. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be obsessed with it. If you're looking for something that looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43900.0,
