    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours condition. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Mechanical provenance is impeccable: the rear subframe has been reinforced, and rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, and the chassis remains rigid and free of corrosion. This is a true purist\u2019s specimen with zero deferred maintenance.",
